THE JITU CUSTOM THEME

## Getting Started

Clone the repositry into the your WordPress Environment under the themes folder

git clone git@bitbucket.org:the-jitu/jitu-marketing-site.git

Activate theme via the wordpress admin dashboard

## Creating Pages

1. Create new page via the admin dashboard
2. Choose the appropriate template
3. Publish your pages
4. View Page

## Creating Navigation Menu

The theme uses wp-navwalker with bootstrap to give a dynamic menu experience
1. Create new menu via admin dashboard
2. Select menu location
3. Add pages or custom URLs
4. Save your work

## Creating page templates

When creating a new page, you need to create a wordpress page template
more info here:- https://developer.wordpress.org/themes/basics/template-files/


## Theme structure
assets 
    css ----------- > page css
    img ----------- > theme images
    js -----------  > javascript files
template-parts ---- > theme template parts (to be included in other templates)
    header -------- > navigation templates-parts
templates --------- > custom page templates
functions.php ----- > controls theme functions
header.php -------- > site header
footer.php -------- > site footer
page.php ---------- > single page template
single.php -------- > Single page template
style.css --------- > Theme entry

## Making commits and PRs
Always create a branch based off master
Always include the ticket number on the PR
Always make a pull request every morning
Make your commit messages clear